Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.58,0:00:03.76,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}阿撒迪斯坦王國 首都
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.31,0:00:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部分軍對發動的政變已被鎮壓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.87,0:00:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但都市區域仍面臨著恐怖襲擊的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.35,0:00:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請各位國民千萬不要外出 選擇呆在家中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿撒迪斯坦第一王女 瑪莉娜·伊斯邁爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 請靜下心來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.76,0:00:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這片真主賜予我們的契約之地上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.90,0:00:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國民之間互相傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是絕不能被容許的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為改革派找來什麼聯合國
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉娜大人 請保佑這孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:55.42,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}阿撒迪斯坦王國 王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:00:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪斯德·拉夫瑪蒂的行蹤還未查明嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.93,0:01:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在與UNION軍配合極力搜尋中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.35,0:01:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看來還要花很長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.02,0:01:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在情況一團糟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.12,0:01:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接收天線被摧毀 聯合國的技術人員也撤走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且連「天人」也來介入
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.02,0:01:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要挽回眼下的情勢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能找到瑪斯德·拉夫瑪蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這條路了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿撒迪斯坦王國
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗教領袖瑪斯德·拉夫瑪蒂的綁架事件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.52,0:01:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引發了內亂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當這場內亂發展成軍事政變階段時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天人」使用Gundam採取了武力介入行動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.76,0:01:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒有戰術預報員皇·李·諾列嘉的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.91,0:01:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那·F·清英和洛克昂·史特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否能阻止阿撒迪斯坦的內亂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三勢力？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了接受阿撒迪斯坦請求的UNION
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和進行武力介入的我們之外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.92,0:02:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有某股勢力誘發了內戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這股勢力綁架了瑪斯德·拉夫瑪蒂？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是我自己的推測
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但Veda也暗示了這種可能性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依據是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在接收天線的建造現場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾遭受過遠距離導彈的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.15,0:02:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從火力情況判斷 對方使用MS的可能性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.06,0:02:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用MS的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我讓剎那去調查了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們在這個國家 太過顯眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據洛克昂的情報 導彈應該就是從這附近發射的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.44,0:03:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殘留反應
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這裏的確曾經有過MS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.11,0:03:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可到底是哪方的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UNION？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和回收的登陸艙一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這反應果然沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也在調查這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PMCtrust方的見解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫拉尼亞紛爭時丟失的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.73,0:03:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷聽可不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當地的孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:04:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我…聽說這附近發生過戰鬥 所以才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個年齡容易好奇 不難理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這一帶還是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快離開這裏比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 會的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於這個國家的內亂 你怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉漢姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼看待這個國家的內亂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法客觀判斷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 你支持哪一方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也不支持
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一方都有自己的正義
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 在這場戰爭中不斷有人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多人會喪命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍人也這麼想？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來這個國家很礙眼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為軍人來得多了 只會增加傷亡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也一樣在戰鬥嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏在背後的是什麼東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片桐 前天從這裏攻擊接收天線的似乎是AEU的最新型機體Enact吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然問這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且聽說這台機體似乎是從莫拉尼亞的PMC搶來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉漢姆 為什麼把這些事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢 就當是說漏嘴好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PMC的Enact…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人和這場內亂有關？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…事到如今還要？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是恐怖襲擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說這一帶改革派居多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS應對不方便 只能請求出動對人鎮壓用的自行機器人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用沒用 這是為了找Gundam出的軍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上層不可能會分派出多餘的戰鬥力來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會打算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受神罰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.99,0:07:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請賜予我們真主的保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:07.46,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 請靜下心來 在這片真主賜予我們的契約之地上…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是何等的無力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打攪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 改革派的爪牙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們必須如此相互仇視呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F3987地點？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏有什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許一無所獲 但有可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總比乾等好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把紅龍也帶上好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很擅長營救要人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN系統休眠解除
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優先權設為剎那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外壁迷彩膜解凍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持GN粒子散佈狀態 進入搭乘模式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 開始執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了沒 紅龍先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames 前往目標地點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這老頭子別說飯了連水都不喝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想接受敵人的施捨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這個國家的人都那麼頑固
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪那個天什麼的搗亂 計劃一團糟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有機影正在接近這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是UNION的偵查嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架白色的MS是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:10:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia到達目標地點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是在這裏麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們帶老頭子走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架Enact
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 機師就是那個庫爾吉斯的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能找到這裏也就不奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到 那時的小鬼居然坐上了Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.47,0:10:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的戰爭還沒結束嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫爾吉斯已經滅亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的真主在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒這個義務
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太浪費了 這機子還是讓給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還算是在意料之中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言之過早吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:11:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 敵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒反應
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.17,0:12:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來技術還沒退步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天人」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天人」？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武力干涉阿撒迪斯坦內亂的私設武裝組織
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:13:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 就是你們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請乘上來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的任務已經接到 皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼作戰行動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這指示真是你發出的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走錯一步的話 Exia就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最切實有效的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贊同皇小姐的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要向世界展示 「天人」的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉娜大人 「天人」發來訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天人」？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經救出瑪斯德·拉夫瑪蒂 正前往王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望皇女盡快召開停戰會議
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 馬上準備進行會談
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的確無法贊同他們的所作所為 也有可能是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我更願意相信他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想相信他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說「天人」正朝王宮來 這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還帶著人質
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若果真如此 是個千載難逢的機會 中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們拭目以待吧 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是阿撒迪斯坦王宮前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:15:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說瑪斯德·拉夫瑪蒂已被救出 並朝王宮前來的市民們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正陸續聚集於此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.74,0:15:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有未經確認的情報說 救出拉夫瑪蒂的是「天人」組織
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam到底是否會在這裏出現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 改革派象徵 瑪莉娜·伊斯邁爾皇女 和保守派宗教領袖卡塔夫的會談如果能夠實現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿撒迪斯坦的國內情勢 將有很大可能朝著結束內亂的方向發展
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開沙慈了啦 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是… 是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.09,0:16:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam正從上空降落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 真的來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.01,0:16:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 Gundam緩慢地在皇宮前著陸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.73,0:16:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然解除了武裝!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太荒唐了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不帶武裝來這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別對Gundam進行攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出契約之地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是槍擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有數位市民正朝Gundam開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam開始有動作了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢開始靠近王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正一步一步前進
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釋放人質
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釋放人質
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別作聲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請去王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 乘坐起來並不算舒適
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.95,0:18:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請允許我表示感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.27,0:18:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瑪斯德·拉夫瑪蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天人」救出了瑪斯德·拉夫瑪蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並送交王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.23,0:18:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉娜·伊斯邁爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今後的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定我們是否再來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抗爭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你所信奉的真主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉 追擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還能擒獲Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去你去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢那麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會為千夫所指的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼 嚇出一身冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個問題會就此解決嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.26,0:19:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 人們能夠走向和平的共識
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走向共識
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互讓步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪斯德·拉夫瑪蒂宣稱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綁架人員是僱傭兵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次內亂是被精心策劃的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而幕後勢力的真正目的 是為了阻止阿撒迪斯坦的現代化的變革
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但並沒有人公開表示對此負責
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.51,0:20:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉娜·伊斯邁爾和瑪斯德·拉夫瑪蒂以共同聲明的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.54,0:20:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼籲國民結束內戰以及恐怖活動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 阿撒迪斯坦的內亂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今仍然持續著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三大國家群體的協同軍事演習中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏的紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縈繞在奔赴戰場的Meister心頭上的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 決意的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是Gundam的話…

